<DOCHDR>
http://health.nyam.org:80/aidsnyc/natap/drug/rtazt3tc.html 199.29.141.24 19970121124504 text/html 11751
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 12:38:58 GMT
