<TR>
<TD><B><FONT SIZE=-1>Division of Nutrition, NYS Department of Health</FONT></B></TD>

<TD><B><FONT SIZE=-1>(518) 458-6868</FONT></B></TD>
<TR></TABLE></CENTER>

