Telephone:  212/255-3841, ext. 22</FONT></TD>
<TD><FONT SIZE=-1><B>MANHATTAN CAB</B><BR>
Clinical Directors Network<BR>
8 West 19th Street, 8th Floor<BR>
NY, NY 10011<BR>
<I>Contact</I>: Steven Long<BR>
Telephone: 718-901-3619</FONT></TD>
</TABLE>

<p>Refreshments are served at each CAB meeting. Travel costs may be provided as necessary.</p>

<p>Community Advisory Boards are coordinated by the Clinical Directors Network of Region II, Inc. (CDN). Each CAB is an independent organization lead by CAB members, elected by CAB members.  CDN provides support for the CABs and the CABs provide advice on CDN's HIV/AIDS activities.</p>

