<td colspan="2"><font size=-1>apples, pears, peaches radish asparagus<br>starfruit, cherries leeks succotash grapes, raisins eggplant cucumber<br>fruit cocktail green string beans beets<br>V-8 juice yellow wax beans lettuce<br>pineapple, bananas, onions mushrooms<br>watermelon, corn, green peas<br>figs cabbage parsnips<br> prunes, soursop okra plums, apricots lychee</font></td>
<p>
<td><font size=-1>2 or more</font></td>
<p></tr>
</table></center>

