<font size=-1>

<p><font size=+1><b>Job Posting</b></font></p>

<table>
<tr>
<td><b>Job Title</b>:</td><td>Development Associate</td>
</tr><p><tr>
<td><b>Department</b>:</td><td>Development</td>
</tr><p><tr>
<td><b>Supervisor</b>:</td><td>Associate Director of Development</td>
