<DOCHDR>
http://health.nyam.org:80/aidsnyc/ai/adult.html 199.29.141.24 19970121130023 text/html 17178
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 12:54:27 GMT
