<DOCHDR>
http://health.nyam.org:80/aidsnyc/pwac/editor.html 199.29.141.24 19970121130224 text/html 8234
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 12:56:31 GMT
