<DOCHDR>
http://health.nyam.org:80/aidsnyc/pwac/manage.html 199.29.141.24 19970121130302 text/html 14920
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 12:57:08 GMT
