<DOCHDR>
http://health.nyam.org:80/aidsnyc/network/lared/simple/ester.html 199.29.141.24 19970121131217 text/html 6299
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 13:06:26 GMT
