<DOCHDR>
http://health.nyam.org:80/aidsnyc/network/lared/simple/indi.html 199.29.141.24 19970121131332 text/html 8680
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 13:07:39 GMT
