<h2 align=center><img align=center src="gifs/ivbotpil.gif" alt="[IV/bottle/pill]" hsapce=10>Should I Join an AIDS Drug Trial?<br>
<font size=3>a handbook from the<BR> 
<a href="index.html">AIDS Treatment Data Network</a></font></h2>

<blockquote>

