<DOCHDR>
http://health.nyam.org:80/aidsnyc/network/simple/three.html 199.29.141.24 19970121134434 text/html 6935
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 13:38:39 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.1
Last-modified: Wed, 21 Aug 1996 16:08:58 GMT
Content-type: text/html
